description: The island has entered Phase Four of its exit strategy, six weeks ahead of schedule.
title: Coronavirus: Guernsey speeds up easing of lockdown
title_page: Coronavirus: Guernsey speeds up easing of lockdown - BBC News
maintext: Deputy Soulsby added: "We are conscious that people are desperate to travel to meet new babies that have been born during lockdown or to see relatives who don't live in the Bailiwick."
